            <div class="svc-text-col">
              <div class="svc-detail-label">Holistic body treatment</div>
              <div class="svc-detail-text">Osteopathy treats the entire body as a connected system. Spinal blockages cause muscle tension, headaches, shoulder and back pain. Vertebral restrictions can lead to digestive disorders and heartburn. Pelvic torsion causes menstrual and bladder dysfunction. Manipulation uses measured movements of varying speed, force, and distance to reposition joints, reducing pain and restoring flexibility and alignment. Dr. Saad holds a Master's degree in Manual Therapy and Osteopathy.</div>
